Package: rarefyr
Title: Lightweight Rarefaction Curves and Plots for Microbiome Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Toryn", "Poolman", email = "t.poolman@ucl.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A small, teaching-oriented package for computing and
    plotting rarefaction curves from OTU/ASV count tables. Designed to
    be readable and hackable rather than exhaustive -- a lightweight
    alternative to pulling in vegan/phyloseq just for a rarefaction
    plot in a teaching context.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tibble,
    ggplot2,
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
